This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: life bliss
des:
This Skill gathers information such as your age and how long you are sitting at your work per day. Based on these two parameters, LifeBliss will analayse and prepare a set of recommendations for you. This is not a medical consultation, but life hack tips for healthy living

Ask alexa as follows,

"alexa ask lifebliss for fifty years " - This will confirm your age and ask you again for your total hours at work were you sit in your seat.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
